1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with human pose estimation in still images using convolutional neural networks. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes semi- and weakly-supervised learning schemes for human pose estimation. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with developing models for pose estimation using machine learning techniques. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with processing and analyzing images. 
5. cs.RO (Robotics) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with estimating human poses, which can be useful in robotics applications.
